text: Aruna Mishra is a female Indian boxer. Her career highlights include gold medals in the 2003 Asian Championships, 2004 World Cup and the 2011 World Police and Fire Games.Aruna punches away to 4th gold ==References== Category:Indian women boxers Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Welterweight boxers
